## Backups

* restic --help

## Formatters

* jq file.json
* fq . file (Binary file)
* htmlq `curl --silent example.com | htmlq 'body' | bat --language html`
* gron `gron "https://api.github.com/repos/tomnomnom/gron/commits?per_page=1" | fgrep "commit.author"`
* fx `curl "https://api.github.com/repos/tomnomnom/gron/commits?per_page=1" | fx` 

## Tree

* alder
* tre

## Calculators

* bcal (Byte calculator)
* pcalc (Byte calculator)
* ipcal (CIDR IP calculator)
* sipcalc (CIDR IP calculator)


