# Networking

## Ping
prettyping example.com

## Geofetch
iponmap 54.247.127.254

## Traceroute
mtr -z facebook.com

## File with data operations

* miller - like awk, sed, cut, join, and sort for name-indexed data such as CSV and tabular JSON.
(https://miller.readthedocs.io/en/latest/quick-examples.html)

## Colors

## Colorized output

echo $(ansi --yellow WARNING:) This is warning

## ZZComplete

Complete options from manual pages

* press Ctrl-F to start the completer

## Screenshots & Recordings

* terminalizer (Record terminal)
* carbon-now -h Script.sh (Create screenshot of source code in Script.sh file)

